Package edu.uw.cp520.scg.domain

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Account
    Defines an account as having a name and being either billable or no-billable, all accounts must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientAccount
    A billable Account that additionally has client contact information and an address.
    Consultant
    A consultant for the SCG, just has a PersonalName.
    ConsultantTime
    A consultants time, maintains date, skill, account and hours data.
    Invoice
    Invoice encapsulates the attributes and behavior to create client invoices for a given time period from time cards.
    InvoiceLineItem
    Encapsulates a single billable item to be included in an invoice.
    TimeCard
    Represents a time card capable of storing a collection of a consultant's billable and non-billable hours for a week.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NonBillableAccount
    Accounts which can not be billed - non-billable accounts, such as sick leave, vacation, or business development.
    Skill
    Skill that a client may be billed for, consists of a name and an hourly rate.
